lopment Studies; Master Degree ( Gender) ; Studying towards Master in Public Management and Policy Planning.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"top\"><strong>Career<\/strong><\/td>\n<td valign=\"top\">Receptionist at Cash Trade Wholesalers 1994 \u2013 1995; Project Leader of the San Poverty Alleviation Project in Tsumkwe 1995; Regional Development Planner for the Food For Work Programme in Otjozondjupa Region 1996 \u2013 2001; Professional Registered Nurse at Roman Catholic Hospital 2005; Head Community Development Officer at Otjiwarongo Municipality 2005; Secretary General of National Youth Council of Namibia 2006 -2008.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Interests<\/strong><\/td>\n<td valign=\"top\">Sport; Debating; Singing<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Member of Parliament &#8211; National Assembly Address: Private Bag 13323, Windhoek SWAPO Party Legislative Profile Member of Parliament since 2008; Deputy Minister of Youth National Service Sport and Culture (2012 &#8211; 2015), Deputy Minister of Health and Social Services since 2015 Personal Born on 21 August 1974 at Otjiwarongo, Otjozondjupa Region Education Started Sub A&hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3598,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","dt_team_category":[105,104,92],"class_list":["post-3631","dt_team","type-dt_team","status-publish","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","dt_team_category-5th-national-assembly-2010-2015","dt_team_category-6th-national-assembly-2015-2020","dt_team_category-7th-national-assembly-2020-2025","dt_team_category-105","dt_team_category-104","dt_team_category-92","description-off"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team\/3631","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/dt_team"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.parliament.na\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/dt_team"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,